title: Black Virginia student bloodied during arrest files $3 million lawsuit
text:
Published By: Reuters - US News - Today 
RICHMOND, Va. (Reuters) - A black University of Virginia student bloodied during an arrest caught on video filed a $3 million civil lawsuit ...
